metadata.description: A ramshackle collection of warehouses and cargo bays on the city's waterfront. The docks are home to El Doria's naval fleet, as well as a thriving black market for illicit goods and services.
metadata.atmosphere: Cramped, squalid, with an air of perpetual chaos.
metadata.significance: A hub for smuggling and trade, where the rules of society are ignored in favor of profit and survival.
